89455
) was recorded as follows (translated from Hamad 
2009
): Dorsal surfaces with alternating crossbands from anterior head to tip of tail; transverse bands Yellowish Olive- Green (
50
), alternating with Olive-Yellow (
52
) bands with Straw Yellow (
56
) mottling, which grade into Turquoise Blue (
65
) and Straw Yellow (
56
