55
), Greenish Olive (
49
), and Paris Green (
63
); lateral surfaces of head Spectrum Yellow (
55
), Turquoise Blue (
65
), and Sulphur Yellow (
57
), extending over ventral surfaces of head and body posteriorly to midventer; then grading into Beige (
219
D) that continues to ventral surface of base of tail; tail thereafter with Sepia (
219
) and Raw Umber (
23
) crossbands; dewlap Cream (
84
) with longitudinal Orange-Yellow (
